data.description: Very nice Village unit with a great location and extra parking right in front of the unit. Just steps from the Somersett town center with pools, par 3 golf and work out facility. There are also 3 restaurants and a convenience store within walking distance. This unit is in great shape and features nice and private courtyard for enjoying the sunsets. Other than the 3 bedrooms there is a loft area that would make a very nice and spacious office. The family room features a fireplace and is open to the dining. Don't miss out on this one! "Open house Saturday Jan 25 from 12-3:00"
